        "richtext_4kMHBj": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Our pieces are symbols of love, commitment, and the moments that matter most.<br/><br/> That's why we obsess over <strong>every detail. </strong><br/>So each and every piece is made to be kept <strong>forever.</strong><br/><br/>Every piece is hand-set by our<strong> master jewellers</strong>, backed by a 5-year warranty, and made to the best-in-class standards of the National Association of Jewellers. <br/><br/><em>A </em><em><strong>promise</strong></em><em> you can trust.</em></p>"
