    "tabs_6cKtj8": {
      "type": "tabs",
      "blocks": {
        "tab_LAczMQ": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "The Promise Standard",
            "content": "<p>The best metals. Precision electroplating. Sealed with an anti-tarnish e-coating. <br/><strong>Six people check every piece </strong>by hand before packaging.<br/><br/>Your piece arrives in packaging chosen and assembled with the same care. Including a <strong>Promise Card</strong>, a keepsake for the words that matter most.<br/><br/>And if you ever need us, we're here. Every message answered within four hours, on average. We are <strong>rated 4.94 stars</strong> from over 430 customers.<br/><br/>Excellence isn't something we aim for. It's the only standard we know.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        },
        "tab_zHpMGK": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "5 Year-warranty",
            "content": "<p>Your jewelry is more than an accessory - it’s a symbol of love, commitment, and life’s cherished moments. That’s why every piece comes with a <strong>5-year warranty</strong> for complete peace of mind.<br/><br/>We’ll <strong>repair</strong> any manufacturing faults free of charge or <strong>replace</strong> your piece if a repair isn’t possible.</p><p>If your warranty has expired, or any accidental damage has occurred please reach out. We’ll still do our best to help with <strong>repairs or replacements at a reduced fee</strong>.</p><p><a href=\"https://thepromiseco.com/pages/2-year-warranty\" title=\"https://thepromiseco.com/pages/2-year-warranty\">View full warranty details here.</a></p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        },
        "tab_xAYzVd": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Crafted By Hand",
            "content": "<p>Every piece is designed in-house and hand-set by our master jewellers, one stone at a time - never glued. </p><p>That's the difference between jewellery that looks good on day one and jewellery that still looks perfect years later.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        },
        "tab_Xp6TKY": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "our precious metals",
            "content": "<p>Our<strong> sterling silver</strong> is 925 certified, crafted with 92.5% pure silver and 7.5% alloys for enhanced durability and a lasting, brilliant shine.</p><p>Our <strong>gold vermeil</strong> uses a thick layer of 18k gold over sterling silver, creating a rich lasting finish. Our plating is up to 25 times thicker than standard gold-plated jewellery.</p><p><strong>Rhodium Plating </strong>applied to sterling silver. Rhodium is one of the world’s most precious metals, known for its mirror-like shine and exceptional resistance to tarnishing.</p><p>Every design is then sealed with an<strong> anti-tarnish e-coating</strong>, adding an invisible layer of protection to preserve its beauty over time.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        },
        "tab_xwFx4K": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "conflict-free simulated diamonds",
            "content": "<p>Our stones boast a 2.18 refractive index (often called the sparkle score), MOHS rating of 8.5 (often called the durability score). </p><p>To compare: Diamonds have a 2.41 refractive index and MOHS rating of 10. </p><p>Swarovski Crystals sit at around 1.6 refractive index, MOHS 6–7.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        }
      },
